TextEng: Me need healing.
I need healing.
Who you be?
Who are you?
Me not understand 'bout Stone of Recall and teleport portal.
Text: 나 귀환석이랑 순간이동 차원문 이해 못 해.

TextEng: Teleportation portal? Stone of Recall? I don't understand.
Text: 순간이동 차원문? 귀환석? 이해가 안 돼요.

TextEng: That's handy.
Me need you go over that one more time.
Text: 나 한 번 더 설명해줘야 돼.

TextEng: Can you explain that again?
Goodbye.
Me need to return to mission. Me need to go back to place where me died.
Text: 나 임무로 돌아가야 돼. 나 죽은 곳으로 다시 가야 돼.

TextEng: How me get here?
I need to return to my mission. I must get back to where I just was.
Text: 임무로 돌아가야 해요. 방금 있던 곳으로 다시 가야 해요.

TextEng: What you suggest?
What do you suggest?
Me think you're right. Goodbye.
I think you're right. I'll see you later.
Text: 당신 말이 맞는 것 같아요. 나중에 봐요.

TextEng: Teleport portal? Recall Stone? What you be talking about?
Text: 순간이동 차원문? 귀환석? 너 무슨 말 하는 거야?

TextEng: Teleportation portal? Stone of Recall? What are you talking about?
Text: 순간이동 차원문? 귀환석? 무슨 말씀을 하시는 거예요?

TextEng: That's handy.
You got bad attitude. Me want go back now!
Text: 너 태도 나빠. 나 지금 돌아가고 싶어!

TextEng: Save the sarcasm and just get me back there.
Text: 비꼬는 건 그만두고 그냥 나를 거기로 돌려보내요.

TextEng: Me change my mind. Goodbye.
I've changed my mind. I'll see you later.
Yes. Me want to go back now.
Yes. Transport me there now.
Just do it.
How did I get here?
Me no trust you Recall spell! You take spell off me now!
Text: 나 귀환 주문 믿지 않아! 너 주문 지금 풀어!

TextEng: You say me be fully healed?
Text: 너 나 완전히 치료됐다고 말한 거야?

TextEng: I don't want your stupid Word of Recall spell teleporting me anywhere. Cancel the spell, right now!
Text: 귀환의 언령 주문이 나를 어딘가로 순간이동시키는 건 원하지 않아요. 지금 당장 주문을 취소해요!

TextEng: How me get back where me be before?
Text: 나 어떻게 전에 있던 곳으로 돌아가?

TextEng: So how am I supposed to get back to where I was?
Text: 그럼 어떻게 원래 있던 곳으로 돌아가야 하나요?

TextEng: You mean I'm fully healed?
Me no remember you cast spell on me.
Text: 나 네가 주문 시전한 거 기억 못 해.

TextEng: How come I don't remember you casting a Recall spell on me?
Text: 귀환 주문을 시전한 걸 왜 기억하지 못하는 거죠?

TextEng: Who you be?
Who are you?
